{"tid":1645322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國文宣組請入","createTime":"2019-10-11T00:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T10:19:47.000Z","uid":51933,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b24129e910aaf9d8ed37bc590cd94508eab77c","tid":1645322,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:26:49.000Z","msg":"有關最近暴雪加上NBA既news, 以下有少少自己既睇法<br />\n=========================================<br />\n呢兩單正正係真正connect國際既news<br />\n好多人好貼地, 但係只係貼自己國家既地<br />\n<br />\n你問下出面D人知唔知伊拉克 土耳奇, 發生緊咩事, 佢答唔答到你?<br />\n但係你搞到NBA , 幾多美國人睇?<br />\n你搞到暴雪, 幾多美國人玩WoW? Diablo? Overwatch? etc..<br />\n佢地就會開始注視有關香港既事, 但係呢個只係開始<br />\n<br />\n你要佢地由頭睇, 邊個會主動搵返6 7 8 9 月既news, 只會睇最新個D<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而呢家正正係文宣需要做個整合, 懶人包, 比美國人睇</span></span></strong> (當然係英文版)<br />\n<br />\n而正當美國民眾都開始理解, 明白發生緊咩事, 自然會支持, 當地議員, 議會, 變相出聲幫手都容易好多, 因為大家都明白刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n以上都需要時間去發生 但係絕對需要文宣組幫幫手!!<br />\n<br />\n========================================="},{"pid":"85c595b23ad952a05e845da9f2402740d67a7b90","tid":1645322,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"6ab6afa597cbfab22156e33022327308151facd4","tid":1645322,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"16852f780716fc379efe2d48d5a54c4c18da96d3","tid":1645322,"uid":313681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"10月12反蒙面法遊行<br />\n<br />\n15:00pm集合<br />\n尖沙咀鍾樓-&gt;深水埗運動場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Nd-f9lZBFn9kArxeYtYKmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNd-f9lZBFn9kArxeYtYKmQ&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=2dfcb725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Nd-f9lZBFn9kArxeYtYKmQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTcLS71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https